5VHY-1HR","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":6565,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/jihad-hajj-mabrur-best-iman\/","url_meta":{"origin":6563,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Struggle: Jihad, Hajj among best deeds after faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked, \u201cWhat is the best deed?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFaith in Allah and His Messenger.\" It was said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cJihad in the way\u00a0of Allah.\u201d It was said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cA blessed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15508,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/go-to-hajj-with-wife\/","url_meta":{"origin":6563,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Go perform pilgrimage with your wife","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA man should not be alone with a woman, nor should a woman travel unless a guardian is with her.\u201d A man stood up and said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I have been assigned to a military expedition,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36569,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/03\/jihad-no-war-combat-killing\/","url_meta":{"origin":6563,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Jihad for women without fighting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is jihad a duty upon women?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYes, jihad is a duty upon them in which there is no fighting: the Hajj and 'Umrah pilgrimages.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 2901 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33178,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/11\/faith-jihad-hajj-best-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":6563,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Deeds: Faith, Jihad, Hajj better than all other deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ma\u2019iz al-Tamimi reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked, \u201cWhich deeds are best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFaith in Allah alone, then jihad, and then a blessed pilgrimage are better than all other deeds like the distance between the rising of the sun and its setting.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6574,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/18\/hajj-pilgrimage-pure-sin\/","url_meta":{"origin":6563,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Pilgrimage: Successful Hajj completely purifies from sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever performs the Hajj pilgrimage to this house, without having intimate relations or committing sin, he will return pure of sin like the day he was born from his mother.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1819, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1072,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/10\/28\/virtue-ten-days-of-dhul-hijjah\/","url_meta":{"origin":6563,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dhul-Hijjah: Virtue of ten days of Dhul-Hijjah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 28, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"No good deeds are better than what is done in these first ten days of Dhul-Hijjah.\" Some companions of the Prophet said, \"Not even jihad\u00a0in the way\u00a0of Allah?\" The Prophet said, \"Not even jihad\u00a0in the way\u00a0of Allah, except\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6563","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonl